author: Thoughty2
description: Five million years ago, Earth accidentally handed whales the ultimate power-up. Ocean currents shifted, nutrients exploded to the surface, and suddenly rorqual whales found themselves in an all-you-can-eat buffet stretching across the planet. Their secret weapon? Lunge-feeding — a move so absurdly effective it turned them from “pretty big” to “record-breaking giants.” No myths, no legends, no secret tournament of sea monsters — just physics, plankton, and one evolutionary jackpot.
title: Why Whales Suddenly Got Huge
